                  <TD valign="middle" height="50" colspan="5">
                    <span id="_ctl0_cpheadcontent_d1_TitleLabel" class="Title">复兴高级中学各处室完成办学规划情况及新规划工作设想（德育）</span></TD>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <TD valign="middle" align="center" height="48"></TD>
                  <TD colspan="2" align="center" valign="middle">
                    <div align="right">索引号：
                        <span id="_ctl0_cpheadcontent_d1_CatalogNum">101340201002-2008-003</span>          
